Package: DaymetR
Title: Batch download single pixel or gridded DAYMET data
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: "Koen Hufkens <koen.hufkens@gmail.com> [aut, cre]"
Description: Functions to (batch) download single pixel DAYMET data
    (http://daymet.ornl.gov) directly into your R workspace, or save them as
    csv files on your computer. Both a batch version as a single download
    version are provided. In addition, code is provided to download gridded
    data for a region of interest specified by a top left / bottom right
    coordinate pair or a single pixel location.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.5)
Imports:
    sp,
    rgeos,
    rgdal,
    downloader
License: AGPLv3 + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
